{"tid":2239542,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有時寧願遇到freerider，都唔想遇到豬隊友","createTime":"2020-10-12T04:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T16:29:18.000Z","uid":305711,"like":75,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c1ae2fccdde9fbf4ad96165bbb5831bebd2dc5c0","tid":2239542,"uid":305711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"遇到Freerider雖則個workload大好多，但起碼做到自己standard嘅野<br />\n<br />\n遇到豬隊友，雖然知佢好努力做份project，但份project叫佢做A，佢就做B，做咗d唔關事嘅野，好懷疑佢有冇聽書同睇ppt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我叫佢改，但佢唔明點解要改，我又要解釋，解釋完，佢改啦，但改完又唔係果回事，又要解釋再解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時真係好想自己幫助直接改晒佢，但組員又覺得自己白費心機，又會覺得我搶晒d野黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有冇咁嘅經歷，歡迎黎圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431041f3a9faf6108257692e5aad156238d1c4fb","tid":2239542,"uid":197157,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:24:10.000Z","msg":"試過，通常最後都係自己做埋佢算<br />\n但係認真咁講<br />\n其實佢聽唔明你想點，你都有責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單講即係你哋溝通得唔好"},{"pid":"9125fc041f8a658ff8b86004604225415e1d2a77","tid":2239542,"uid":305711,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"431041f3a9faf6108257692e5aad156238d1c4fb","tid":2239542,"uid":197157,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:24:10.000Z","msg":"試過，通常最後都係自己做埋佢算<br />\n但係認真咁講<br />\n其實佢聽唔明你想點，你都有責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單講即係你哋溝通得唔好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:28:06.000Z","msg":"我同其他組員解釋完，佢地做自己個part完全冇問題，就係佢講極都唔明，可能我真係要諗吓辦法，再詳細d解釋比佢嘅